BTCServ is a free for all [[Mining Pool|Pooled_Mining]] with Pay-Per-Share [[Bitcoin]] rewards located in Germany. The pool has launched on July 9th, 2011 and is steadily growing since then. Its features are native [[Long_Polling]], SSL encrypted user interface with user statistics, mobile website and fast payouts.

at feburary of 2012 the pool got hacked and 400BTC was stolen, since that it is offline


#### FEE
BTCServ does not charge a fee, it offers the user to set up automatic donations which support the pool.

